### Get all vehicles for a specific driver
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/driver/{{driverId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}

###

### Update a vehicle
PUT {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/{{vehicleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "CAR",
  "model": "Camry",
  "color": "Black",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Delete a vehicle
